                    <tr>
                      <td width="100%"><font face="arial" size="2">Many of the trade skill are getting revamps and updates. For example the prices of alchemy items were just cut in half this last patch and poison is scheduled for a revamp soon. What are things you would like to see in your favorite trade skill? What is your favorite trade skill? Is it profitable? What do you think about trade skills being worked into some of the newer quests?</font>
                        <p>&nbsp;
					  </td>
                    </tr>
