						The raw materials for trade skills are much too high to ever be able to make a profit.  You should be able to sell successful trade items back to NPCs and at the very least recover the cost om materials.  It would still be expensive to learn a trade because you fail a lot.  I like Smithing but I will never recover to PPs that it cost me to learn.<p>At Master skill level I can make banded for only a little more than the materials cost.  THat is if I want to stand around half the night waiting for someone who wants to buy and then waining for the to go to the bank.<p>
						
						</font>
